##OpenGL GLIB
Perspective 70.
LookAt 0 0 3  0 0 0  0 1 0

Vertex		noise.vert
Fragment	noise.frag
Program Noise						\
		uAd <.01 .05 .5>			\
		uBd <.01 .05 .5>			\
		uTol <0. 0. 1.>				\
		uKa <0. 0.1 1.0>			\
		uKd <0. 0.6 1.0>			\
		uKs <0. 0.3 1.0>			\
		uNoiseAmp <0. 0. 1.>  		\
		uNoiseFreq <0. 1. 10.>		\
		uShininess <0.5 10. 50.>	\
		uUseXYZforNoise	<false>	
		
Color 1. .9 0
Sphere 1.0 50 50
Sphere 0.5 50 50
